Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rage on! Rage on! Rage on! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:21.50,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Moeagare! Moeagare! Moeagare GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must run forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:27.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo hashire
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,If you are still burning with furious rage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.29,0:00:34.76,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Mada ikari ni moeru toshi ga aru nara...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must fight the towering foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.93,0:00:38.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kyodai na teki o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fight! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.39,0:00:41.47,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uteyo! Uteyo! Uteyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Bring to bear the rage of justice, Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:48.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Seigi no ikari o butsukero GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:54.61,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Rise once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.07,0:00:58.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru! Yomigaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Rise once more! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This G-Fighter is made up entirely\Nof the new Gundam parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We've had Ms. Sayla piloting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we've had no technical problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.48,0:01:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If we separate the G-Fighter\Nand insert Gundam in between...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...we get the G-Armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...which is a combination of the Gundam\Nwith all the new parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.72,0:01:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem is, we haven't been able\Nto test a mid-air docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla isn't used to it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no problem separating\Nthe parts from the Gundam in mid-air.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,At this speed, I think we'll be able\Nto do it even during battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.41,0:02:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The laser sensor alignment\Nneeds to be refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.54,0:02:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I gotta go to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.31,0:02:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,- Make it quick.\N- Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Our main problems with its usage\Nare in these following areas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The G-Sky is formed by adding the G-Parts'\Nrear engine to the Core Fighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it can be used as\Na long-range fighter-bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.70,0:02:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But it uses the bottom half of the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...so while the G-Sky's in action,\Nthe Gundam is disabled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'd mostly use the\NEZ form of the G-Sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It can use any Core Fighter from\Nthe Guncannon or Guntank.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.21,0:02:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gotta be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.21,0:02:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's dock the G-Bull into the G-Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.43,0:02:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,These shields, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:03:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The main goal of these new parts\Nis to strengthen the Gundam's armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.73,0:03:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you think about the moment\Nwhen it converts into the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...you have to remove the shields.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So what we need to do is develop\Na joint to link the two shields together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And we'll also need at least twice\Nas many supply parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.16,0:03:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, we'll be unable to make\Nthe best use of our one Gundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they'll live on this ship\Nfor the rest of their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.94,0:03:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spy on Board
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have them work on technical\Nimprovements as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When the White Base's\Nengine maintenance is complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...you will head to Federation Forces\Nheadquarters in South America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.98,0:03:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will return to the frontlines\Nin Europe. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.26,0:03:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All rise! Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.20,0:04:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And... give my regards\Nto those three little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mr. Shiden is going to leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where is he gonna go?\N- How should any of us know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he really is leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.73,0:04:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- Repair it quickly.\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ask the Colonel!\N- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.02,0:04:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai...! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.42,0:04:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's inevitable. All those military formalities\Njust don't suit me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I like everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're comrades,\Nwho have been through so much together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I like the way you put that, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.02,0:04:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.17,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him do as he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.17,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.55,0:05:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If you push yourself too much,\Nyou can't win battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I've decided to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The Zeons are pushing themselves hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I've just gone past my limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take this along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You should be able to sell it for some cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.21,0:05:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's your toolbox, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.10,0:05:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need money, no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.76,0:05:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say I like everything about you either.\NBut, I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a pleasure. Thanks for everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.87,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Stay alive, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You also think he's a coward,\Ndon't you, Mirai?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The second ship is carrying a Z'Gok...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,...an amphibious heavy mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're extremely reliable.\NBut this ship only has one Gogg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.59,0:06:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Have them stop\Nthe Trojan Horse leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the Trojan Horse leaves the dock,\NI want to know where it's heading.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! I've already got someone working on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Think I should start a hardware store?\NEh, Amuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.36,0:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.30,0:06:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.16,0:06:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've been\Nthrown off the warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have a place to stay, do you?\NCome stay at my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.42,0:06:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean it?\NSo there must be a catch, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.08,0:06:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.44,0:06:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind if it's only for a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Miharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I live with my little brother and sister.\NYou don't mind, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So the three of you are hiding\Nin an abandoned house?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,- Welcome home, sis!\N- Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,- Were you good?\N- Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. He's gonna be our guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, how do you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.86,0:07:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- About the warship you were on...\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's quite something, isn't it?\N- I guess so. You like ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.98,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, growing up by the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.20,0:07:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, even though the White Base is a ship,\Nit's technically more of a space warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's a spaceship.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.64,0:08:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Just worrying about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably tired.\NRest for a while, I'll go get you a blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make yourself at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem well trained.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.74,0:08:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. If he leaves the house,\Nyou let me know right away, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,- Mhm.\N- We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sorry to be a bother!\N- Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the White Base\Nis leaving tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.22,0:08:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They're having issues with\Nthe starboard engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If they took a hit in that spot,\Nthe ship would likely be stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:09:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel, having to take care\Nof your younger brother and sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.66,0:09:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain.\NThere's a message from No. 107, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's in contact with\Na Trojan Horse crew member.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.20,0:09:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, the Trojan Horse is having\Nproblems with its starboard engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.43,0:09:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,- Understood.\N- Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,- Captain.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.81,0:09:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Exactly where is No. 107 situated?\N- The same harbor as the Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,While we attack with the Gogg...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,...have No. 107 sneak aboard\Nthe Trojan Horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like to cover all possibilities.\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you do succeed,\NI will expedite your return to Zeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.77,0:09:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Please return to the Mad Angler, Captain.\NI'll pull this one off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I am counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,- Have the Mad Angler prepare for backup.\N- Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.52,0:09:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ship No. 2, launch Z'Gok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's going smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.17,0:10:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This machine suits me much\Nbetter than the Gogg.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.82,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've lost response from Area 29.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Unknown. It's faster than the previous ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.66,0:10:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the crew to stand by to intercept!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.90,0:10:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Take off at once?! It'll take us a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Send out the Guncannon and Guntank!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.75,0:10:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How about the G-Fighter or G-Sky?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- The voltage is a little irregular, but it's fine.\N- Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is using Freeze Gel\Nso you can't pursue them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our job to get past it and destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.50,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to fire anti-submarine missiles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Activate the harbor's defenses\Nand synchronize sonar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will begin our attack on the enemy\Nat the exact moment the Z'Gok reaches land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Connolly, use that diversion to get to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,CC2 received from Callahan\Nin the Z'Gok!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Launch the backup Gogg\Nand then surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch Connolly's boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.55,0:11:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the dock's gate okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Just break through it.\NIt'll be no problem with the armor on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say.\NHas the Guntank already left?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.10,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no. The shaft isn't operating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The repairs are done, so please get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.14,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!\NGundam taking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!\NThe Gundam will ride on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.64,0:12:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,An air raid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The White Base is being attacked?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It seems too soon the Zeons herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.98,0:12:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did your sister go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.72,0:12:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-She'll be back in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, she went shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Did she really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... It's the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll believe you.\NWhatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like they're attacking from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Gimme back my bicycle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for military use, you'll get it back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Greetings! Are you in a big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.56,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no! No, I'm not in any hurry, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you call me out to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. There's money in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your orders are to infiltrate the Trojan Horse\Nand find out where they're heading to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.23,0:13:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Figure that out for yourself.\NJust sneak in by any means necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a lot here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll do it, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear there'll be more money in it\Nif you succeed. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In this bag you'll find\Na Federation Forces uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the captain's letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do something to feed my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.88,0:13:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great. Well, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the silhouette,\Nit looks like the Gundam and a fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.50,0:14:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the forward Gogg to start attacking!\NPrepare for anti-air combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Please be careful!\NThere might be more than one ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.49,0:14:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll attack the closest submarine\Nwith the G-Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.36,0:14:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,- Were you afraid?\N- We were fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,- How's he doing?\N- He took his stuff and left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.16,0:14:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.79,0:14:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,- He said, "Best of luck."\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Best of luck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, listen, you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Sis has to go to work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.76,0:15:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I could be gone for a bit longer\Nthis time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Use this money carefully while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Never tell anyone where the money is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm done with this job, let's go\Nsomeplace where there's no war, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to be patient.\NI know how strong you two are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.54,0:15:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sis, you have the same nice smell...\N...just like Mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.67,0:15:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.40,0:15:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit is approaching\Nfrom the rear at 4 o'clock, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.57,0:15:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Hayato?!\NLaunch the Guncannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.60,0:16:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm leaving now! Is the beam rifle ready?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hayato! Guncannon, launching!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.13,0:16:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with me now.\NAll that shooting and exploding.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.64,0:16:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon! Now! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.27,0:16:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's too accurate with his shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the infamous Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.19,0:16:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't measure up to the rumors!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't concern me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.44,0:16:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But... you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.67,0:16:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I worrying about\Nthe White Base after all those?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Coward!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... maybe I really am a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the same trick again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.27,0:17:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! How's the battle going for you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro! Please return!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mobile suit is attacking Hayato's{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Sayla In the G-Fighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.78,0:17:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got an anti-submarine attack plane{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, those guys are so slow...\Nit's impossible for me to sit back and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.75,0:18:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! I'm with the military! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to the base to pick it up later. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.59,0:18:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Guntank... where's the Guntank?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is! What's it doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Kai! Please use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We just finished the repairs on its shaft!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hayato's in the Guncannon now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I'm not gonna let you get any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He's persistent. In that case...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tear you apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.81,0:19:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I've taken so much damage,\Nthere's no power left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.69,0:19:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What? A tank?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll lure the tank into the water\Nand take care of it out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.85,0:20:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna fight underwater\Nwhere you've got the advantage?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sayla here. I sank the enemy ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this one is the real Gundam,\Nbut I'll finish it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.15,0:21:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Here he comes...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.17,0:22:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The remaining ship has retreated!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.50,0:22:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Check all sections!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as we're done with\Nthe engine maintenance, we're taking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.14,0:22:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Amuro.\NI was told your toolbox isn't worth a dime.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.65,0:22:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.96,0:22:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh, hello, Kai. Welcome back.\N- Hi, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stand watching you all struggle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right, Hayato?\N- Sure, whatever you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.12,0:22:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Spy No. 107\Nmade it on board the Trojan Horse...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.96,0:22:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However the enemy did manage to sink\None Gogg and one Z'Gok.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.42,0:22:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. That sounds about right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Boone's problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.54,0:22:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Have him make arrangements\Nto contact our spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.96,0:22:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Later that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...the White Base left the demolished town...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...with a spy on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.92,0:23:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Char's relentless pursuit\Nshows no signs of letting up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As they face many dangers...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.62,0:23:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kai and Miharu's growing friendship\Ncomes to a tragic end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.72,0:23:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could possibly speak the words...\N"Miharu, rest in peace"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.84,0:23:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NAcross the Atlantic Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.34,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Across the Atlantic Ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
